@startuml "Ionosense HPC - Executive Summary"
!theme plain

' ---- styling ----
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontSize 16
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam rectangleBorderThickness 3
skinparam arrowThickness 4
skinparam roundCorner 25
skinparam shadowing true
hide stereotype

' ---- colors (no leading # in values) ----
!define PRIMARY   2E86AB
!define SUCCESS   52B788
!define WARNING   F77F00
!define HIGHLIGHT FCB322
!define LIGHT     EDF2F4

title <b>Ionosense HPC: Next-Generation Ionospheric Research Platform</b>\n<i>Accelerating Discovery Through High-Performance Computing</i>

' ============================================================================
' Research Vision
' ============================================================================
rectangle "**RESEARCH VISION**\n\nEnable comprehensive ionospheric analysis\nat unprecedented speed and scale" as Vision <<Vision>> #LIGHT

' ============================================================================
' Three Pillars
' ============================================================================
together {
  rectangle "**SPEED**" as Pillar1 #SUCCESS
  note bottom of Pillar1
    <b>100–1000× Acceleration</b>
    ────────────────
    Before: 2 weeks
    <b>Now: 1 hour</b>

    Real-time capable
  end note

  rectangle "**SCALE**" as Pillar2 #PRIMARY
  note bottom of Pillar2
    <b>Handle Big Data</b>
    ────────────────
    Process TB datasets
    10,000+ FPS

    Months of data in hours
  end note

  rectangle "**SCIENCE**" as Pillar3 #HIGHLIGHT
  note bottom of Pillar3
    <b>Research Excellence</b>
    ────────────────
    Reproducible
    Collaborative

    Publication-ready
  end note
}

' ============================================================================
' Research Impact Areas
' ============================================================================
package "**RESEARCH IMPACT**" <<Impact>> #LIGHT {

  rectangle "**Ionospheric Scintillation Studies**\n\n✓ Multi-scale temporal analysis\n✓ Equatorial & polar phenomena\n✓ Real-time detection\n✓ Pattern discovery" as Impact1 #E8F5E9

  rectangle "**Space Weather Monitoring**\n\n✓ Continuous observation\n✓ Anomaly detection\n✓ Predictive capabilities\n✓ Risk assessment" as Impact2 #E8F5E9

  rectangle "**GNSS Signal Analysis**\n\n✓ Navigation safety\n✓ Communication integrity\n✓ Infrastructure protection\n✓ Quality metrics" as Impact3 #E8F5E9
}

' ============================================================================
' Success Metrics
' ============================================================================
rectangle "**SUCCESS METRICS**\n\n<b>Research Productivity</b>\n• 10× more experiments per month\n• 100× faster hypothesis testing\n• 50% reduction in time to publication\n\n<b>Computational Efficiency</b>\n• 90% reduction in processing time\n• 10× reduction in energy usage\n• Linear scaling with data size" as Success #F0F8FF

' ============================================================================
' Competitive Advantage
' ============================================================================
rectangle "**COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGE**" as Advantage #FFFACD
note right of Advantage
  <b>Why Ionosense HPC?</b>

  <font size="18">✓</font> <b>Only platform</b> with real-time ionosphere capability
  <font size="18">✓</font> <b>Fastest</b> FFT processing (GPU-optimized)
  <font size="18">✓</font> <b>Complete</b> workflow automation
  <font size="18">✓</font> <b>Full</b> reproducibility guarantee
  <font size="18">✓</font> <b>Open source</b> and extensible

  <b>Result:</b> <font color="green"><b>Lead the field in ionospheric research</b></font>
end note

' ============================================================================
' Call to Action
' ============================================================================
rectangle "**NEXT STEPS**\n\n<b>Get Started Today</b>\n1. Deploy platform (< 30 minutes)\n2. Run example experiments\n3. Import your data\n4. Accelerate your research\n\n<b>Support Available</b>\n• Documentation\n• Example workflows\n• Community forum" as NextSteps #SUCCESS

' ============================================================================
' Relationships
' ============================================================================
Vision --> Pillar1
Vision --> Pillar2
Vision --> Pillar3

Pillar1 --> Impact1
Pillar2 --> Impact2
Pillar3 --> Impact3

Impact1 --> Success
Impact2 --> Success
Impact3 --> Success

Success --> Advantage
Advantage --> NextSteps

' ============================================================================
' Strategic Value Box
' ============================================================================
note top of Vision
  <b><font size="20">Strategic Research Value</font></b>
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  <b>Grant Competitiveness:</b> Demonstrate cutting-edge computational capabilities
  <b>Publication Impact:</b> Process larger datasets, discover new phenomena
  <b>Collaboration Potential:</b> Share reproducible workflows globally
  <b>Future-Proof:</b> Scalable to next-generation datasets
end note

' ============================================================================
' Bottom Line
' ============================================================================
center footer <b><font size="20">Bottom Line: Do More Science, Faster</font></b>\n<font size="14">Production Ready • Open Source • Proven Performance</font>

@enduml
